claim: “Cocaine kills coronavirus, scientists are shocked to discover that this drug can fight the virus.”
explanation: This “breaking news” image is from an online news generator and not based on any real news coverage.

claim: A viral image suggests that cocaine kills coronavirus.
explanation: According to the WHO, there is no cure for the new coronavirus.
There’s no scientific evidence to support this theory. In fact, there is still no cure for the COVID-19.
Fake story was generated by a website that allows people to create their own news stories. This is a previously disproved claim.
The claim is false. There is no vaccine or medical treatment available for COVID-19. Cocaine is a stimulant and an addictive drug.
